The paper introduces a traffic flow model for autonomous UAVs, which involves modeling individual vehicle motions and the capacity of flow. This suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA), Robotics (cs.RO), and Systems and Control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the analytical solvability of the model, which could place it under Information Theory (cs.IT) or Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE).
